reviewText: Bach keyboard concertos of the highest audio and visual quality.  One thing that I didn't like was the 2 performances of the 4-keyboard concerto, albeit with different pianists; I'd have preferred to have another concerto included.  The improvisations by Gabriela Montero are a nice addition to the collection.  177 minutes of magnificent performances!
AMAZING DVD-set. I like Bach*s music a lot and I find these concerts amazing... Such a lovely music, performed by such a big persons! I recommend.
